{"tid":1198072,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(商科人請入) 擠提攻擊討論","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T03:04:35.000Z","uid":25367,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd40ed7bbdd1f1a56a584af5bbb76fd05023d016","tid":1198072,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"今日見唔同post都有巴打提到呼籲公眾提款引發擠提，不如集中討論認真下可行性? 我對經濟認識唔多，以下係我嘅理解，希望巴打們補充<br />\n<br />\n《金融數據月報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/market-data-and-statistics/monthly-statistical-bulletin/table.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fmarket-data-and-statistics%2Fmonthly-statistical-bulletin%2Ftable.shtml&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=6fecfde7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/market-data-and-statistics/monthly-statistical-bulletin/table.shtml</a><br />\n1. 根據《流通貨幣》3月數據, [認可機構持有的法定紙幣及硬幣] 為26,097百萬，代表<ins>一百萬人每人由銀行提款26,097，銀行現金就會清空</ins>?<br />\n2. 根據《流通貨幣》3月數據, [認可機構持有的法定紙幣及硬幣] 加 [由公眾持有的法定紙幣及硬幣] 等於 26,097百萬 + 484,487百萬 = 510,584百萬。但根據《貨幣統計數字 》3月數據, [流通紙幣及硬幣] 為505,974百萬。 銀行現金+公眾現金 唔等於 流通現金?<br />\n3. 假設銀行港元現金為零，但仍存有外幣現金及債券等，銀行會否即時宣告破產?<br />\n4. 假設銀行港元/外幣現金為零，但仍存有債券，銀行會否即時宣告破產?<br />\n<br />\n《香港存款保障委員會》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dps.org.hk/tc/coverage.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dps.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fcoverage.html&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=731df70f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dps.org.hk/tc/coverage.html</a><br />\n5. 香港有五十萬港元存款保障，代表銀行破產後由香港政府支付最高五十萬元補償，所以<ins>大量銀行可以間接削減政府庫房儲備</ins>?<br />\n<br />\n《本財政年度首個月（即截至二零一九年四月三十日）的財務狀況》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201905/31/P2019053000315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201905%2F31%2FP2019053000315.htm&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d6da7fc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201905/31/P2019053000315.htm</a><br />\n6. 四月底政府財政儲備為1,176,510.3百萬， 而《金融數據月報》{銀行體系統計數字} 所有認可機構的客戶存款 為13,741,978.385百萬，遠高於政府儲備，所以最理想情況下能利用存款保障淘空庫房，使政府破產?<br />\n<br />\n綜合<br />\n7. 擠提攻擊應以銀行/政府為攻擊目標? 應主張 <ins>提取銀行所有存款</ins> 抑或 <ins>利用存款保障等政府賠償</ins>?<br />\n8. 呼籲公眾提款是否犯法?<br />\n9. 擠提攻擊能否有效迫使臨奠撤回惡法?<br />\n10. 擠提攻擊對中國/外國有否影響?"},{"pid":"4726570451c7e33a498c11ec77f7d0725e2eed44","tid":1198072,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"e000b1120aae2bafd63c8e7639df1cc570417673","tid":1198072,"uid":249903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"IT狗搭唔到咀，睇到push下，有興趣"},{"pid":"3e9072912d3fc8dc38cd9dccec7ef642f1e801b9","tid":1198072,"uid":187232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4726570451c7e33a498c11ec77f7d0725e2eed44","tid":1198072,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">噚日遊行完真係令人好不安<br />\n覺得香港好無前途<br />\n依家仲發現連燈有好多人諗住用財技去做抗爭<br />\n真係諗起都驚驚地<br />\n不由自主去咗ATM撳咗1萬蚊砸袋傍身<br />\n吖今日有成100萬人遊行<br />\n人人都好似我咁，銀行咪好大鑊<br />\n呢個世界有樣嘢叫擠提<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f27cbe49398b5c0b2bad6bd625a68a8af22dbac5","tid":1198072,"uid":77813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20080926/11649106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20080926%2F11649106&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d44a73c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20080926%2F11649106&h=706ce763\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk