%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fkey-functions%2Fmonetary-stability%2Fliquidity-support-to-banks.shtml&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d228f974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-functions/monetary-stability/liquidity-support-to-banks.shtml</a><br />\n大商家支持可參考08年東x銀行事件<br />\n<br />\n3. 支持修例嘅人都可以號召去存錢托儲備金，不過上面都講過金管局一個都夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：有多啲創意想法係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9cffbc34bdcab09d5d6cd417391ee427ced7be","tid":1198072,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無，唔洗唸<br />\n無翻一百幾廿億都唔會整得爆hsbc 同 bochk"},{"pid":"2b04c303365c0a786866ea5860fa5205c1a59000","tid":1198072,"uid":128151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e58f0ac4493b6621150e35f4b481ab94b94cb19","tid":1198072,"uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"用英文bank run可能容易啲理解，多數係出於市民對個別銀行現金儲備有擔心，所以狗衝去攞返哂現金<br />\n以下假設所有反修例人士提哂自己啲錢而又唔怕南亞佬係tm附近護送佢地<br />\n1. 如果並非銀行管理有問題，就算銀行唔夠現金，都可以係銀行體系入面借到錢渡過緊張期<br />\n<br />\n2. 由於銀行係too big to fail，未免影響經濟同自己生意，政府金管局、大商家到時一定會存錢入去托住個儲備現金（唔係送錢俾銀行，係存錢），如果市面唔夠現金，金管局可以用外匯基金印，而且金管局有責任同能力去泵錢俾銀行，可以參考<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-functions/monetary-stability/liquidity-support-to-banks.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fkey-functions%2Fmonetary-stability%2Fliquidity-support-to-banks.shtml&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d228f974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-functions/monetary-stability/liquidity-support-to-banks.shtml</a><br />\n大商家支持可參考08年東x銀行事件<br />\n<br />\n3. 支持修例嘅人都可以號召去存錢托儲備金，不過上面都講過金管局一個都夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk