-30T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"商科人，半個會計佬，我對銀行運作認識唔大，我只用常理推斷。<br />\n可以先集中於所有中資銀行先。但中資銀行應該主要服務大機構，大陸人，當中有幾多個香港人又願意參加今次行動呢？<br />\n冇記錯香港銀行間應該有d機制當出現大部份資金離開時可以向其他銀行借錢。對現金只佔銀行的極少部份總金錢, 有冇類似的機制呢？我唔肯定。<br />\n可行性唔大，但都係不合作運勳之一來的，應唔應該推唔推我不評論。"},{"pid":"196d9ecc9f2b48ab36f0f42abc83ac5e2639ebfe","tid":1198072,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人到而家仲未識真正咁運用三角鐵馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267307\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkrd2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkrd2R.gif&h=d8974866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkrd2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkrd2R.gif&h=d8974866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkrd2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkrd2R.gif&h=d8974866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keuoggc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeuoggc.gif&h=0ba950e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keuoggc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeuoggc.gif&h=0ba950e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keuoggc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeuoggc.gif&h=0ba950e7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}